  "instructions": [
    "Season the oxtail with flour, shaking off excess. Set aside.",
    "Heat the olive oil in a large Dutch oven over medium-high heat.",
    "Sear the oxtail until browned on all sides. Remove from pot and set aside.",
    "Add the onion, garlic, and ginger to the pot. Cook until the onion is translucent.",
    "Add the shio-cure, keto-friendly ketchup, allspice, and thyme to the pot. Stir to combine.",
    "Add the rum to the pot, stirring to deglaze.",
    "Return the oxtail to the pot, and pour in enough water to cover.",
    "Bring to a boil, then reduce heat to low and simmer for 2 hours, or until the oxtail is tender.",
    "Season with salt to taste.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with chopped fresh herbs, if desired."
  ],
